relative flex h-2 w-2\"><span class=\"absolute inline-flex h-full w-full animate-ping rounded-full bg-green opacity-75\"></span><span class=\"relative inline-flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green\"></span></span>Live · 1,300+ tools</div><h1 class=\"text-4xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl animate-fade-in-up delay-100\"><span class=\"gradient-text\">Connect your agent</span><br/><span class=\"text-text-primary\">to every tool it needs.</span></h1><p class=\"mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed text-text-secondary md:text-lg animate-fade-in-up delay-200\">Discover, inspect, and execute any tool with one balance. No subscriptions. No API key sprawl. Just code.</p><div class=\"mt-10 animate-fade-in-up delay-300\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-xl rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-elevated p-1 shadow-2xl shadow-accent/5\"><div class=\"rounded-lg bg-bg-card p-5\"><div class=\"mb-3 flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-[#ff5f57]\"></div><div class=\"h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-[#febc2e]\"></div><div class=\"h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-[#28c840]\"></div><span class=\"ml-2 text-xs text-text-muted\">aegntic-cli</span></div><div class=\"code-block space-y-1 text-left\"><div><span class=\"text-text-muted\">$</span> <span class=\"text-green\">aegntic</span> <span class=\"text-accent\">discover</span> <span class=\"text-text-muted\">-q</span> <span class=\"text-amber\">&quot;twitter posts&quot;</span></div><div class=\"mt-2 text-text-muted\"><span class=\"text-text-secondary\">12 tools found</span><span class=\"text-text-muted\"> · ranked by fit &amp; price</span></div><div class=\"mt-1 text-text-muted\">  1. <span class=\"text-text-primary\">twitter/search</span><span class=\"text-text-muted ml-2\">$0.001/call</span><span class=\"ml-2 text-green\">✓</span></div><div class=\"text-text-muted\">  2. <span class=\"text-text-primary\">twitter/timeline</span><span class=\"text-text-muted ml-2\">$0.002/call</span><span class=\"ml-2 text-green\">✓</span></div><div class=\"text-text-muted\">  3. <span class=\"text-text-primary\">twitter/user-tweets</span><span class=\"text-text-muted ml-2\">$0.001/call</span><span class=\"ml-2 text-green\">✓</span></div><div class=\"mt-1\"><span class=\"text-text-muted\">$</span> <span class=\"text-green\">aegntic</span> <span class=\"text-accent\">run</span> <span class=\"text-amber\">&quot;twitter/search&quot;</span> <span class=\"text-text-muted\">--param q=&quot;AI agents&quot;</span><span class=\"inline-block h-4 w-2 animate-pulse bg-accent align-middle\"></span></div></div></div></div></div><p class=\"mt-8 text-sm text-text-muted animate-fade-in-up delay-400\">Give this to your agent —<!-- --> <code class=\"rounded border border-border bg-bg-card px-2 py-0.5 font-mono text-xs text-text-secondary\">$ set up https://aegntic.ai/SKILL.md</code> <!-- -->— and let it take it from there.</p></div></section><section class=\"px-6 py-16\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-6\"><div class=\"group relative flex flex-col items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-border-subtle bg-bg-card p-5 transition-all duration-200 hover:border-border hover:bg-bg-card-hover\" style=\"animation-delay:0ms\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-xl text-sm font-bold text-white transition-transform duration-200 group-hover:scale-110\" style=\"background-color:#1d9bf0\">X</div><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-sm font-medium text-text-primary\">X / Twitter</div><div class=\"mt-0.5 text-xs text-text-muted\">scraping</div></div></div><div class=\"group relative flex flex-col items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-border-subtle bg-bg-card p-5 transition-all duration-200 hover:border-border hover:bg-bg-card-hover\" style=\"animation-delay:50ms\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-xl text-sm font-bold text-white transition-transfo